headline: Aflac turns checkered pattern into a powerful reminder to "Check for Cancer"
summary: Aflac, a leading provider of cancer insurance for nearly 70 years, working with sports broadcaster, fashion entrepreneur and cancer survivor Erin Andrews, today launched Check for Cancer, a national movement aimed at boosting U.S. cancer screening rates by 10% over the next decade.
